    <title>Next主题配置</title>
    <link href="https://vuhks.github.io/[object%20Object]/Next%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>https://vuhks.github.io/[object%20Object]/Next%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</id>
    <published>2020-05-27T17:16:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-06-07T14:03:07.509Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="修改next主题文件-config-yml"><a href="#修改next主题文件-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="修改next主题文件_config.yml"></a>修改next主题文件<code>_config.yml</code></h1><p><a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/getting-started/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考https://theme-next.js.org/docs/getting-started/</a></p><h2 id="添加CDN连接"><a href="#添加CDN连接" class="headerlink" title="添加CDN连接"></a>添加CDN连接</h2><p>修改<code>mediunzoom :true</code>然后使用默认配置</p><h2 id="next方案选择"><a href="#next方案选择" class="headerlink" title="next方案选择"></a>next方案选择</h2><p>在<code>scheme</code>关键字来更改方案<br>默认方案是mise</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">schme: Muse</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="启用暗黑模式"><a href="#启用暗黑模式" class="headerlink" title="启用暗黑模式"></a>启用暗黑模式</h2><p>主题NexT会根据系统模式自动切换至黑暗模式</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">darkmode: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="修改站点语言"><a href="#修改站点语言" class="headerlink" title="修改站点语言"></a>修改站点语言</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">language: zh-CN</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置头像"><a href="#配置头像" class="headerlink" title="配置头像"></a>配置头像</h2><p>侧边栏显示头像</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">avatar:</span><br><span class="line">  # Replace the default image and set the url here.</span><br><span class="line">  url: &#x2F;images&#x2F;avatar.gif</span><br><span class="line">  # If true, the avatar will be dispalyed in circle.</span><br><span class="line">  rounded: false</span><br><span class="line">  # If true, the avatar will be rotated with the cursor.</span><br><span class="line">  rotated: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
