    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="什么是Markdown"><a href="#什么是Markdown" class="headerlink" title="什么是Markdown"></a>什么是Markdown</h1><p>markdown一般以.md结尾<br>#Markdown的基本语法<br><a href="https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/Markdown-Cheatsheet" target="_blank" rel="noopener">markdown基础语法</a></p><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><ol><li>有序列表</li><li>无序列表<br>. 无序列表<br>. 有序列表<h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h2><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/05/28/tVkqDU.jpg" alt="tVkqDU.jpg"><h2 id="超链接"><a href="#超链接" class="headerlink" title="超链接"></a>超链接</h2><a href="https://vuhks.github.io">vuhks</a><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[vuhks](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;vuhks.github.io)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="加粗、斜体"><a href="#加粗、斜体" class="headerlink" title="加粗、斜体"></a>加粗、斜体</h2></li></ol><p><strong>加粗</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**加粗**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>斜体</em></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**加粗**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="字体颜色和字号"><a href="#字体颜色和字号" class="headerlink" title="字体颜色和字号"></a>字体颜色和字号</h2><p><font face="宋体" color="red" size="18">你好，测试</font></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">"宋体"</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">"red"</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">"18"</span>&gt;</span>你好，测试<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="居中"><a href="#居中" class="headerlink" title="居中"></a>居中</h2><center><font face="宋体" color="red" size="18">你好，测试</font></center><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">"宋体"</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">"red"</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">"18"</span>&gt;</span>你好，测试<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>## 居右<p align="right"><font face="宋体" color="red" size="18">你好，测试</font></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">"宋体"</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">"red"</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">"18"</span>&gt;</span>你好，测试<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
